Bruschetta

Yield: 8
Time: 30m
Author: name
Tags: italian

Ingredients
  - ciabatta, 1
  - olive oil, 3 tablespoons
  - garlic, 2 cloves
  - tomatoes, 6
  - basil, 8 stems
  - parmesan, grated: 75 g
  - vinegar, balsamic: 2 tablespoons
  - salt
  - pepper

Instructions
  - Mix tomatoes, garlic, basil, vinegar, olive oil, parmesan, salt and pepper.
  - Wait for at least 15 minutes.
  - Slice the ciabatta bread into pieces put the mixture on top.
